text: Malaa, Moses ga daahi dana dogodogo gi di langi, gei Dimaadua ga dugu ia nia atili mo dono uwa hadu magalillili, gei ogo di ila gu dabadaba gi di gelegele. Dimaadua ga hagau mai dana madangi maaloo mono ila ala e mamaahina gi mua mo muli. Deenei hua di uwa hadu huaidu ne hai i hongo Egypt, digi hai loo beelaa mai loo i taamada.9.23-24 Hagagida 8.7; 16.21
